{"tid":863642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港女變老，會惡頂嗎？","createTime":"2018-10-15T18:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T21:46:32.000Z","uid":140967,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"805f0e5421363f6e1546f8c9b972db5f5e915419","tid":863642,"uid":140967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T18:38:13.000Z","msg":"宜家班年輕人，尤其係港女<br />\n<br />\n生活多姿多彩，成日飲飲食食旅行影靚相擺ig<br />\n<br />\n但人終會有老既一日，到左呢代港女去到六七十歲，衰老晒走晒樣<br />\n<br />\n到時佢地仲敢唔敢將佢地年輕時既生活放係社交媒體？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當佢地老左，性格依然咁港女，會唔會好怪好惡頂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人老左，社會始終會有歧視，婚姻又未必keep一世，會唔會有部分港女因年紀大會下流做洗碗清潔既工種？"},{"pid":"52e28af31327df07acecdfb4ac3b7a2fd3083083","tid":863642,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"變大媽"},{"pid":"eae3d947d9dcb505512bc8a955be32748c289126","tid":863642,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T19:46:30.000Z","msg":"毒撚一世都無多姿多彩<br />\n諗起將來我𠵱家仲惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091c9316bd686162283bfedc95db8a0fd111b654","tid":863642,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T21:46:32.000Z","msg":"30就見形"}]}